titles.title: A bill to suspend temporarily the duty on keto ester.

action.text: Sponsor introductory remarks on measure. (CR S16455)
Read twice and referred to the Committee on Finance.

bill.summary: 11/19/1993--Introduced. Amends the Harmonized Tariff Schedule of the United States to suspend, through December 31, 1996, the duty on ethyl 2-keto-4-phenylbutanoate (also known as keto ester).
